{"id":267,"date":"2011-12-15T21:36:45","date_gmt":"2011-12-15T20:36:45","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/ah-sp.com\/?p=267"},"modified":"2024-07-08T12:43:49","modified_gmt":"2024-07-08T12:43:49","slug":"walk-to-jumuah-a-hadith-on-earning-years-of-good-deeds","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/abuhakeem.com\/walk-to-jumuah-a-hadith-on-earning-years-of-good-deeds\/","title":{"rendered":"Walk to Jumu&#8217;ah! A Hadith on Earning Years of Good Deeds"},"content":{"rendered":"<div style=\"display:flex; gap:10px;justify-content:flex-start\" class=\"wps-pgfw-pdf-generate-icon__wrapper-frontend\">\n\t\t<a  href=\"https:\/\/abuhakeem.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/267?action=genpdf&amp;id=267\" class=\"pgfw-single-pdf-download-button\" target=_blank><img src=\"https:\/\/abuhakeem.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/free-pdf-download-icon-2617-thumb.png\" title=\"Generate PDF\" style=\"width:auto; height:45px;\"><\/a>\n\t\t<\/div><p>Bismillah Wal Hamdullillah Was Salaatu Was Salaamu &#8216;alaa Rasoolillahi<\/p>\n<p>Ammaa ba&#8217;d:<\/p>\n<p>Upon the authority of Aus Ibn Aus &#8211; Radhiyallahu &#8216;anhu &#8211; that the Prophet &#8211; Sallallahu &#8216;alahi Was Sallam said: &#8220;<em><strong>Whoever makes Ghusl on the day of jumu&#8217;ah and washes well, and leaves out in the early part of the day and proceeds early, and he walks and does not use transportation. Then he\u00a0sits close to the Imaam and he remains quiet and disturbs no one, he will recieve for every step he takes, the reward of a years worth of action, a year of standing in prayer and a year of fasting<\/strong><\/em>!&#8221;<\/p>\n<p>(Collected by At Tirmidhi (496), An Nisaa (3\/95) Abu Daawood (345) and Ibn Maajah (1087) and is declared &#8216;Saheeh&#8217; by shaikh Al Albaani in &#8216;Saheeh Abu Daawood (333)<\/p>\n<p>A tremendous hadeeth establishing tremendous reward for the one who fulfills its conditions, even if a person practices it just once in his lifetime!<\/p>\n<p>Wa Sallallahu &#8216;Alaa Nabiyinaa Muhammad<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/www.twitter.com\/abuhakeembilal\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">www.twitter.com\/abuhakeembilal<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n<p> @abuhakeembilal <\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>This article explores a powerful Hadith describing the immense rewards for walking to Friday prayers (Jumu&#8217;ah). Learn how each step can earn you a year&#8217;s worth of good deeds, prayer, and fasting!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":9028,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"jetpack_post_was_ever_published":false,"_jetpack_newsletter_access":"","_jetpack_dont_email_post_to_subs":false,"_jetpack_newsletter_tier_id":0,"_jetpack_memberships_contains_paywalled_content":false,"_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[22],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-267","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-worship"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"https:\/\/abuhakeem.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2011\/12\/Walk-to-Jumuah.jpg","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/abuhakeem.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/267","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/abuhakeem.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/abuhakeem.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/abuhakeem.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/abuhakeem.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=267"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/abuhakeem.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/267\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/abuhakeem.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/9028"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/abuhakeem.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=267"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/abuhakeem.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=267"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/abuhakeem.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=267"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}